# name: To buy or not to buy
# uuid: buying-decision
# key: trigger-key
# condition: t
# --

** To buy or not to buy
1. Can I afford it?
2. Is this a need or a want?
3. What do I need to cut from my budget to make room for this?
4. Will this add value to my life?
5. Will I actually use this item?
6. How long will this item last?
7. Do I love the item or the price?
8. Is this item more than I need?
9. Can I borrow this item from a friend?
10. Am I getting the best deal?
11. Will this cause clutter and chaos later?
12. Do I have to buy this today?